{
  "stem": "26486.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were saying, in French, [SPEAKING FRENCH] And then one of them grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She said, they're going to come and beat you up and they're going to maybe kill you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Keep quiet.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Don't say-- so they put me in bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And once I got in bed-- back in the bunker with them, that I calmed down, and my-- my delirium sort of passed, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I wanted my mother and-- I wanted my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Poor mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She waited for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Remember when I-- well, you're not to the liberation, but when I was liberated, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she was jumping with joy, so much that at the train station in Paris-- because I was liberated in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They brought me back to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And John and his nephew came to wait for me at the air-- at the airport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were several of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I wasn't alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when we got there, there were hostess ladies, hostess to give us flowers, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we weren't-- we weren't dressed very nice because they'd taken our uniform off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But in Sweden, they gave us other clothes, but not things that were very fancy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Anyway, when I got there-- and poor-- they were both John.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "His nephew and him were both John.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they looked at me, and they said, oh, poor Mickey.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We have to go and get you some clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they want to make like a joke of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But anyway, when I got there, then they had re-- reserved a hotel, a whole suite.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And John had put downstairs, 'forbidden to have visits.' I was too weak.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
